schools.name: Amy Biehl Community School At Rancho Viejo

data.description: This gorgeous property is located in the highly sought after Rancho San Marcos Equestrian Community containing 15.84 +/- Acres with spectacular views of the surrounding  Ortiz mountains.  The home consist of 2100 +/- square feet with large windows to view the surroundings from the comfort of your interior space.  The home features three bedrooms and two full bathrooms with a large walk in closet and jacuzzi tub in the master and an additional room that could be used for an office or art studio.  A large dining room situated between the living room and kitchen offers you ample room to entertain and enjoy the views.  Home also includes a laundry room and a spacious two car attached garage with a attic for extra storage.  A few steps out the back door sits your very own drive through barn with three separate horse stalls with outside access to runs.  The large sliding doors allow for easy transport through the barn with stalls on one side and a heated tack room/work shop  and hay storage on the other.  The property is on it's very own private well and conventional septic system.  Don't miss out on this gorgeous property and book your appointment today.
